# RESTful API Design

## Router štruktúra

```javascript
import express from 'express';
import { query } from '../db.js';
import { authRequired } from '../auth.js';

export const dogsRouter = express.Router();

// Aplikuj auth na všetky routes v routeri
dogsRouter.use(authRequired);
```

## CRUD Endpointy

| Method | Path | Popis | Response |
|--------|------|-------|----------|
| GET | `/dogs` | Zoznam (s filtrom) | `[{...}, {...}]` |
| GET | `/dogs/:id` | Detail jedného | `{...}` |
| POST | `/dogs` | Vytvorenie | `{...}` (201) |
| PUT | `/dogs/:id` | Update | `{...}` |
| DELETE | `/dogs/:id` | Zmazanie | `{ ok: true }` |

## Vzor GET list s filtrom

```javascript
router.get('/', async (req, res) => {
  try {
    const search = req.query.search || '';
    const like = `%${search}%`;
    
    const { rows } = await query(`
      SELECT * FROM items
      WHERE ($1 = '' OR name ILIKE $2)
      ORDER BY updated_at DESC
      LIMIT 50
    `, [search, like]);
    
    res.json(rows);
  } catch (error) {
    console.error('Get items error:', error);
    res.status(500).json({ error: 'Internal server error' });
  }
});
```

## Vzor POST create

```javascript
router.post('/', async (req, res) => {
  try {
    const { name, ...rest } = req.body || {};
    if (!name) return res.status(400).json({ error: 'name required' });
    
    const { rows } = await query(`
      INSERT INTO items (name, ...) VALUES ($1, ...)
      RETURNING *
    `, [name, ...]);
    
    res.status(201).json(rows[0]);
  } catch (error) {
    console.error('Create item error:', error);
    res.status(500).json({ error: 'Internal server error' });
  }
});
```

## Vzor PUT update

```javascript
router.put('/:id', async (req, res) => {
  try {
    const { rows } = await query(`
      UPDATE items SET name = $1, updated_at = now()
      WHERE id = $2
      RETURNING *
    `, [req.body.name, req.params.id]);
    
    if (!rows[0]) return res.status(404).json({ error: 'Not found' });
    res.json(rows[0]);
  } catch (error) {
    console.error('Update item error:', error);
    res.status(500).json({ error: 'Internal server error' });
  }
});
```

## Vzor DELETE

```javascript
router.delete('/:id', async (req, res) => {
  try {
    await query('DELETE FROM items WHERE id = $1', [req.params.id]);
    res.json({ ok: true });
  } catch (error) {
    console.error('Delete item error:', error);
    res.status(500).json({ error: 'Internal server error' });
  }
});
```

## Error responses

- `400` - Bad Request (chýbajúce/nevalidné dáta)
- `401` - Unauthorized (nie je prihlásený)
- `404` - Not Found
- `500` - Internal Server Error

Vždy vráť JSON objekt s `error` kľúčom: `{ error: 'popis chyby' }`
